reviewText: love it, its my favorite show
I have lots of fun watching the episode. It takes longer time as I thought but it is very entertaining . doesn't get tired watching it.

My wife loved this TV show.  Giving her this Volume will make her very happy.  Too bad that Amazon sells this only through a vendor.  This would be a huge seller.  The series is still ongoing and I would be buying the rest of the volumes in the future.  She would enjoy it more if we can get the rest of the volumes.
